{"type": "article", "id": 21629, "title": "这家瑞士的医院，令人想起平静的蓝色湖水", "description": "圆弧处理和飞翔的象征，带给病人平和放松的心情和对生命的希望。", "date": "2016-02-02T08:00:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 17008, "name": "公共建筑"}, {"id": 2297, "name": "医院"}, {"id": 3835, "name": "瑞士"}, {"id": 22949, "name": "meier + associés architectes"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 158, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607131335nobKdfgc5rjNmsPe.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>洛桑(Lausanne)是瑞士的第二大城市，洛桑大学医院在去年完成了肿瘤调养中心和职工餐厅的改建。</p>\n<p>这两幢建筑都是两层楼，属于原有医院的副楼，通过走廊相连。两排长条形的玻璃窗是最明显的特征，使得白色的墙面也被间隔成三段，有点像船舱。两幢楼都是长方形，但在转角处是圆弧形的，看上去很温和。与旁边高大、灰色的混凝土医院主楼略有不同。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131327P9zR4hvetZLXsluq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131327L25FQ4R3mzBYW7ot.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5787037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>肿瘤调养中心接近方形，围着四面墙是一排小房间。走廊的形状和窗户都类似于医院的外观，在转角做了圆弧处理，取代原本尖锐的直角，能让人感到放松。</p>\n<p>中间天井的墙面涂成了蓝色，从屋顶上悬挂了一圈很细的绳索，牵引着白色纸飞机盘旋上升。对应的地板也是蓝色的，像是从湖水中起飞的小鸟。阳光正好从天井里照射下来，四面的窗户都可以看到这些飞翔的小鸟，它带给修养的病人希望的象征。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131328TEDMlbpX1Ar0uW5a.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78518519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131328XBqZsKOo4L6i1eDf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131329Vso0rSUYjagkATP4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131329t7IPXUQKf5VpJ9aC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131330Ar2kjbCweUQKx8XL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131330Al924rL083hCHe1j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131331xIJ1pdBUzMl0ARYn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131331n2Xet8CxbTmJroFs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131332w5MsUlqdibpmKyA6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>餐厅在肿瘤调养中心的后面，是长条形的，为了增加 900个座位而新建。他们在天花板下加建了一层屋顶，却做了三角形的镂空，让白炽灯照射下来，也有飞机机翼的象征。四周的落地窗让餐厅显得明亮，也有很好的视野。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131332TY3RLqeo0l89ShUH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131333amYLotq0GeFDrlv8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131334SocU7rCla0XBVdIe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131334lzWAhwpZ5jo26vun.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure></div>\n<p>二楼是医生的办公室，保留了圆弧的墙面。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131335GHn56EksyjJ1OmBf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自<a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/780922/lausanne-university-hospital-extension-meier-plus-associes-architectes\"> archdaily</a></p>\n\n\n"}